The pytorch code of hyperspectral image super-resolution method SSP-Mamba.

The code will be released after acceptance.

Requirements
Python 3.10
Pytorch 2.1.1
CUDA 11.8
Preparation
To get the training set, validation set and testing set, refer to SSPSR to download the mcodes for cropping the hyperspectral image.

Training
To train SSP-Mamba, run the following command.

sh demo.sh
Testing
run the the following command.

sh test_demo.sh
References
CST:https://github.com/Tomchenshi/CST.git
